title: Joe Biden Gaffe, Middle East Policy
itunes:title: Joe Biden Gaffe, Middle East Policy
description:
Guests include: Max Burns, Democratic Strategist; Senior Contributor at Millennial Politics, Hagar Chemali, CEO of Greenwich Media Strategies and former Treasury spokesperson for Terrorism and Financial Intelligence.

Kevin also spoke about the Trump administration’s Middle East policy strategy with Jason Greenblatt, Special Representative for International Negotiations.
